							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> That the </em><em>Māori Purposes Bill be now read a second time</em><em>.</em></p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 109</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; New Zealand Labour 32; Green Party 14; Māori Party 2; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 12</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand First 12.</p><p class="VoteResult">Bill read a second time.</p></div></body>
